<DOC><DOCNO>  ZF108-687-640  </DOCNO><DOCID>08 687 640.andM;</DOCID><JOURNAL>MacWEEK  July 31 1990 v4 n26 p1(2)* Full Text COPYRIGHT Coastal Associates Publishing L.P. 1990.andM;</JOURNAL><TITLE>Adobe Illustrator 3.0 gets handle on text and charts. (drawingprogram from Adobe Systems Inc.) (product announcement)</TITLE><AUTHOR>Guglielmo, Connie.andM;</AUTHOR><SUMMARY>Adobe Systems Inc announces Illustrator 3.0, a new version of itsdrawing program that gives users improved text-handling features.andO;Illustrator 3.0, $595, is due in Sep 1990.andP;  It will offer a newgraphing and charting tool; an improved interface; and an updatedversion of Adobe Separator, a utility for four-color separation.andO;Included in the purchase price is Adobe Type Manager 2.0.andO;Improvements include the ability to type, edit and manipulate textdirectly on-screen instead of using a text dialog box; capacityfor an unlimited number of characters, styles, sizes and colors oftext in text blocks; the ability to import data and generatecharts from other programs, including Microsoft Excel; and theability to import Adobe Photoshop images as backgrounds.andO;Registered users can upgrade for $99 until Dec 31, 1990.andM;</SUMMARY><DESCRIPT>Company:   Adobe Systems Inc. (product introduction).andO;Ticker:    ADBE.andO;Product:   Illustrator (Computer graphics software) (product enhancement)Illustrator 3.0 (Computer graphics software) (productintroduction).andO;Topic:     EnhancementsGraphics SoftwareProduct Introduction.andM;</DESCRIPT><TEXT>By Connie GuglielmoandM;Mountain View, Calif.andP;  -- Adobe Systems Inc. last week announced a newversion of Illustrator that gives users of the PostScript-based drawingprogram the text-handling features they have been asking for since 1988.andM;Version 3.0, to ship in September for $595, contains a new graphing andcharting tool; a streamlined interface; and an updated version of AdobeSeparator, a four-color separation utility.andP;  The program also comes withAdobe Type Manager 2.0 (see related story, Page 9).andM;&quot;We look at the program now as the only product you would need forsingle-page design,&quot; said Paul Towner, product marketing manager.andM;andgt;Text.andP;  Seasoned Illustrator users should be happy to find that the textdialog box is a thing of the past, Towner said.andP;  The new version lets userstype, edit and manipulate text directly on-screen.andM;The 256-character limit for text blocks has been removed, allowing users toenter and mix an unlimited number of characters, styles, sizes and colorswithin any block.andM;Adobe also is adding automatic kerning, leading, and word and letter spacing.andM;For special effects, text now can be created directly on a curve and movedfreely along the path.andP;  All text, whether within a box or on a path, can bedirectly rotated, skewed and scaled in real time.andP;  Users also can now convertany PostScript font into an outline that can be edited.andM;For text layout, the program supports automatic text wrap around objects.andO;Text also can be flowed from one column to another column or to any othershape.andM;andgt;Charting and graphing.andP;  Users will be able to generate charts and importdata from programs such as Microsoft Excel to automatically generate bar,line, area, scatter and pie charts.andP;  When information is changed inIllustrator's Graph Editor, graphs are automatically updated.andP;  Graphs, whichare created as a grouped object, can be edited using a new direct-selectiontool that lets users select and modify separate attributes within a groupedobject.andM;Graphs can be customized and saved as templates, Towner said.andM;andgt;Interface.andP;  In addition to streamlining dialog boxes, Adobe has altered someof the tools to make them more easily identifiable and has added aninteractive feedback window that informs users which tool has been selected.andM;Other new features include the capability to import Adobe Photoshop images asbackgrounds.andP;  The revamped Adobe Separator now provides file information anda preview of the image to be separated.andM;Registered users can upgrade to Version 3.0 for $99 until Dec.andP;  31; afterthat, the upgrade is $149.andP;  Users who purchase Illustrator 88 between July 1and the ship date will receive a free upgrade.andM;Adobe Systems Inc. can be reached at 1585 Charleston Road, P.O. Box 7900,Mountain View, Calif.andP;  94039; (415) 961-4400.andO;</TEXT></DOC>